name: Coco Round Box L
description: The Coco Round Box Large is a sophisticated and luxurious accent piece with its exquisite quilted details. Available in other sizes and different finishes. Handmade with Shagreen & Bronze-Patina Brass. Wipe clean with soft dry cloth. Made in Philippines. All shagreen-covered items should be kept out of direct sunlight. Color variants may occur on the stingray and other exotic finishes, showcasing the Parisian label's commitment to creating authentic luxurious products using natural components.
